{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_49","type":"agent_message","text":"The condition registrations are only part of the story. The newer failures show Boot configuration machinery is still being skipped, which is consistent with more annotation-driven Boot classes being loaded by name at runtime. Rather than keep guessing one class at a time, I’m using the repo’s metadata-generation path with an expanded Boot package filter under the same GraalVM to capture the exact dynamic accesses this test exercises, then I’ll trim that back into the library metadata."}}
